Installation
============

You can find the installation instructions for this version of piml in the
documentation file `docs/installation.rst`.

Documentation
=============

We currently host multiple versions of the documentation, which includes
installation instructions, at https://github.com/hlxin/piml/docs

You can build a local copy of the documentation for this version of piml.
You will find instructions to do this in the "Documentation" section of the
file `docs/develop.rst`.
